metadata.name: Devil Inside
metadata.description:
Inside my heart like a human but what the surrounding humans treat me Their eyes looked at me with disgust.

I can't go to the barber shop. Because my skin is scary.

I can't go to the luxury restaurant. because I was worried that my skin would affect the environment.

But my skin never harms others.

There is one thing I can say. If I can do, You can do.
